title: COTTAGE CHEESE GELATIN FLUFF
directions: In a medium bowl, mix the cottage cheese and dry jello mix well. Fold in the whipped cream until no streaks of jello remain. Chill well before serving.
Per 1/4 Recipe: 269 Calories; 24g Fat; 9g Protein; 5g Carbohydrate; 0g Dietary Fiber; 5g Net Carbs
Per 1/6 Recipe: 179 Calories; 16g Fat; 6g Protein; 3.5g Carbohydrate; 0g Dietary Fiber; 3.5g Net Carbs
ingredients: 1 small package diet jello, any flavor
1 cup cottage cheese or ricotta cheese
